03:31.503 --> 03:32.796
Did you get that?

03:32.922 --> 03:35.132
Captain McCenzie, do you understand me?

03:35.257 --> 03:37.426
You are to abort this mission.

03:47.770 --> 03:50.856
If you're in trouble and
you can't speak, just cough.

05:36.378 --> 05:38.380
What the hell are you
doing here, soldier?

05:39.131 --> 05:41.050
Where's the rest of your unit?

05:42.468 --> 05:45.763
Listen, these ragheads would
love to slit your throat.

05:45.888 --> 05:48.223
Now, I need to know how
many of you there are

05:48.349 --> 05:51.727
and what you're doing here, so
I can try to save your necks.

05:54.646 --> 05:56.565
You just don't get it, do you?

06:21.673 --> 06:23.342
Let me spell it out to you.

06:24.259 --> 06:27.221
I work for CIA.

06:27.888 --> 06:30.599
I cannot allow one lost soldier

06:30.724 --> 06:33.352
to compromise my entire operation.

06:35.813 --> 06:38.357
Okay, your choice.

06:56.583 --> 06:58.293
You know what I think, soldier?

06:59.461 --> 07:02.589
I think you are dressed like a woman,

07:02.714 --> 07:06.427
because secretly you
don't want to be a man.

07:36.790 --> 07:40.002
Captain McCenzie, your orders are
to stand down. You are not to...

07:40.627 --> 07:44.006
Now, when I'm done cutting you,

07:44.840 --> 07:48.218
these boys will finish
making a woman of you.

07:53.891 --> 07:55.809
Boy, am I glad to see you.

07:56.018 --> 07:56.935
Craig!

08:03.817 --> 08:05.194
You all right?

08:05.486 --> 08:06.612
Oh, man!

08:07.654 --> 08:09.448
My wife is gonna be relieved.

08:09.656 --> 08:11.492
But control is gonna
cut your balls off, man.

08:11.617 --> 08:13.535
That guy was CIA.

08:14.411 --> 08:18.123
It seems to me, you party with the
devil, God ain't ever gonna help you.

08:18.248 --> 08:19.917
Come on, let's go.

09:13.762 --> 09:15.514
