59:28.440 --> 59:29.275
What the fuck happened?

59:29.400 --> 59:31.485
Which one of you is responsible
for giving away our position?

59:31.610 --> 59:34.738
Seemed to me our friends
down there needed some help.

59:48.752 --> 59:50.004
Where's Vanderbeer?

59:50.129 --> 59:52.298
Last time I saw him he was in the...

59:53.799 --> 59:55.593
