01:03:37.689 --> 01:03:39.858
We've got to get back to the group.

01:03:47.658 --> 01:03:50.994
Look, I'm sorry about your brother.

01:03:51.954 --> 01:03:53.747
And I'm sorry about your friends.

01:03:53.872 --> 01:03:57.000
